Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Corpseless{Kabaneri}"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, something between a Corpse{Kabane} and a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... the same as me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it means you're not human!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're saying you're my enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse{Kabane}s are the enemy of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kurusu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...we would all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That does not mean we can have\Nthe Corpses{Kabane} accompany us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will turn everyone here into Corpse{Kabane}s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are—?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Corpseless{Kabaneri}, not a Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body may be a Corpse{Kabane},\Nbut your mind's still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{How can I}You want me to believe—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.20,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ayame-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} goes to Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It does according to its schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's }"Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Warlord{Shogun}'s greatest stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame-sama, if we are heading to Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:30.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,Can you take me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, we promise we'll stay in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm trying to talk—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not leaving this train\Nwhether you agree to it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you human or a Corpse{Kabane}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Corpseless{Kabaneri}!
Comment: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-san, that's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to look at it from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just open the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back this evening with more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this is going to be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is for your unborn baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't enough food and water for\Nthe number of people that are onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last safe place we can go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku} doesn't take us in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have food rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The current elder is Ayame-sama's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not be turned away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have oil all over your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A body mother gave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body's healed, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your body is a Corpse{Kabane}'s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to move around fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you what, but I'm on an important mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you interested in Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}They're at the forefront of Corpses{Kabane} research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}They might be able to do something...\Nabout this Corpseless{Kabaneri} condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}{I thought }Didn't you want to get off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,590)}It's not that I fully believe...\Nyour "Corpseless{Kabaneri}" story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if I'm trapped inside\Nthis boiler car for three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will show that my mind will remain human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll ride the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will be my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When I fight for too long, I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need a living shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you have to worry about\Ngetting bit by a Corpse{Kabane}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stand up.\NWe're going to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Start what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Training, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not much of a shield right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.75,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your motions are too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet are dragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you let the Corpse{Kabane} onto the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We should throw the Corpses{Kabane} off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They promised they would remain in the rear car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a Corpse{Kabane} knows how to keep a promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the Six Chiefs not have\Nany sense of gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that man has tried to do the right\Nthing even before becoming a Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You cannot just barge in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They demand we stop the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to hold a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to pray for our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our prayers will not reach them if we go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want our grandchildren unable to pass on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, how many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You spin around and boom, boom, bam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ju— Just because you can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...your explanation is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already getting overpowered\Nwhen I haven't even removed my restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing around your neck for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the same as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that if I remove mine,\NI can fight at my full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But after a while, the curse spreads and I get tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpse{Kabane}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not supposed to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpse{Kabane} are loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If definitely felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised you were going\Nto stay in the boiler car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for "Corpseless{Kabaneri}."
Comment: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like the Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew not to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Nameless{Mumei}{Anon} back with me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure she cooperates\Nuntil we reach Daimond Citadel{Kongokaku}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can make me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand even if I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We never should have let Corpse{Kabane}s onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's remove them from the train now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got bad news, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the water tank we\Npatched together is busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way it's making it to the next station.
Comment: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gathering water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Check and see if the pressure's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no Corpse{Kabane}s in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}How long do we need in order to repair the water tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}We might be done by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have the lookouts rotate in shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{That is a g}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us hold a vigil since\Nthe Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou} is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For those elderly people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to pray as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have mercy. Please have mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And pretending to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like praying is going\Nto bring them back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose someone too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you particularly close with your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Scumbag.
Comment: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the kind of man I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my family years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty common story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing your family to the Corpses{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that in your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts when I get hit by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a rock you can find around any river.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found two of these pretty rocks with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her she could have both...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she said we should both\Nkeep one as good luck charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I never planned on keeping it as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was f}Five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...{T}the Corpses{Kabane} broke through our station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The adults fled in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And my sister was caught by the Corpse{Kabane}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty common story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do you think her stupid brother did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an excuse about calling for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I ran from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to rely on someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...my sister was lying on the ground,\Nalready beginning to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The cowardly brother cried and apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry. I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it meant dying with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...I should have overcome my fear and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I hate\Nmyself for running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...my sister is never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a pretty common story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the strong survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Corpses{Kabane} are our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they attack us first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to do this, Ayame-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You people...
Comment: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayame-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends are awful jumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want war, I am happy to oblige!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to act brave when you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nameless{Mumei}{Anon}, don't provoke them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones doing the provoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I knew the Corpseless{Kabaneri} were our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to protect our families!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Purification{Rokkon-shoujou}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous, please come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't, Ayame-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother... won't be able to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpseless{Kabaneri}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are jumpy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Comment: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need to go potty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him to laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikoma, you told my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...not to point our guns at the wrong targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the Corpseless{Kabaneri} our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you our allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayame-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As the one left in charge of the Iron Fortress{Koutetsujou}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have to ascertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...who our enemies are, and who our allies are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you using your right arm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just grab and bite me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I made a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it would save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not sacrificing any more lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Corpses{Kabane} who are our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My purpose in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to destroy the Corpses{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who still believe he is our enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...you are welcome to come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall give you the opportunity\Nto check for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry for testing you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you take the blade directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have grabbed my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No... um...{Oh, I can't control} my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been long since I became like this, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was afraid I might have hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not need to be so concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please worry more about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All that laughing made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some dumpling soup{dango jiro}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you a bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The stuff that comes out when you cut someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A Corpseless{Kabaneri}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm half-Corpse{Kabane}, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because of your bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling us to become Corpse{Kabane} too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Kajika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a monster after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault, I got hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Corpse{Kabane}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's... pregnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikoma?!
Comment: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.34,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will remember that day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.76,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Losing myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:16.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,In steam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:24.49,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Countless mistakes are made
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:29.78,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I can't see anything ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:32.54,op/ed,,0,0,0,,You said
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:38.08,op/ed,,0,0,0,,"Ask your own burning blood"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.96,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Answer my beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:51.93,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.31,op/ed,,0,0,0,,And slam everything onto the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:01.65,op/ed,,0,0,0,,My soul is devoted to my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Burn your life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:09.41,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:40.98,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Even if the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:46.53,op/ed,,0,0,0,,That connect you make a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:52.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,There are just dreams in the same rain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:57.46,op/ed,,0,0,0,,And lights are dried up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:02.67,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I am tired of getting answers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.09,op/ed,,0,0,0,,By mimicking others
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:13.51,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Dawn without the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:18.27,op/ed,,0,0,0,,And broken morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:24.44,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Smashed cry and dream\NThe ideal only has its doors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:30.15,op/ed,,0,0,0,,City is uplifted and drown in noise
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:35.54,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will still sing and stop turning the rudder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:42.33,op/ed,,0,0,0,,To hush silence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:31.15,sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC5C4BF&\bord0\fs35\pos(1126,259)\fade(1000,800)}Chapter\NThree
